Name
       reset_max_time_borrow  - Resets the specified maximum time borrow limit
       of the specified objects

Syntax
       reset_max_time_borrow

       <object_list>

       Resets the specified maximum time borrow limit  of  the  specified  ob-
       jects.

Parameters
       <object_list>
              Specifies  the  list of pins, instances, or clocks for which the
              time borrow limit is reset.

